    <innerclass refid="structStmPeriodicTimer_1_1DispatchEntry" prot="private">StmPeriodicTimer::DispatchEntry</innerclass>
    <briefdescription>
<para>STM32 Periodic Timer — wraps TIM_HandleTypeDef for periodic callbacks. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Users configure a hardware timer in STM32CubeMX, then pass the resulting TIM_HandleTypeDef* to this wrapper. The wrapper manages start/stop/period adjustment and dispatches the update interrupt callback to the registered function.</para>
